{
  "page": "Illyrio's plans",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg/350px-Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"286\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg/525px-Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fb/Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg/700px-Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Illyrio_Mopatis_by_JakeMurray_FFG.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a>, by Jake Murray © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Illyrio's plans</b> revolve around the plotting of <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> to presumably restore <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a> rule in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a> appears to be very involved with making plans with Illyrio. Illyrio has made at least one trip to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> to secretly meet with Varys in the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>However, his plans seem to constantly change, fail, and only a few of them come to pass. The <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a> eventually become fed up with Illyrio's seemingly fruitless plans.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_plans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Convinced <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a>, claimant king of Westeros, and his sister <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys</a>, to stay at <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio%27s_manse\" title=\"Illyrio&#39;s manse\">his manse</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Already has in his possession, or procures, three priceless <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_eggs\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragon eggs\">dragon eggs</a> to gift to Daenerys on her wedding day.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Paid <a href=\"/index.php/Triarch\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Triarch\">Triarch</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Nyessos_Vhassar\" title=\"Nyessos Vhassar\">Nyessos Vhassar</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Elephant_party\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Elephant party\">elephant party</a> enough to own him eight times over.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_plans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_plans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Daenerys_Targaryen_by_Vanessa_Cole.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/df/Daenerys_Targaryen_by_Vanessa_Cole.jpg/300px-Daenerys_Targaryen_by_Vanessa_Cole.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"413\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/df/Daenerys_Targaryen_by_Vanessa_Cole.jpg/450px-Daenerys_Targaryen_by_Vanessa_Cole.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/df/Daenerys_Targaryen_by_Vanessa_Cole.jpg/600px-Daenerys_Targaryen_by_Vanessa_Cole.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Daenerys_Targaryen_by_Vanessa_Cole.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> with one of the three <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_eggs\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragon eggs\">dragon eggs</a> gifted to her by <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a>, by Vanessa Cole ©</div></div></div>\n<ul><li>Plot to marry Princess Daenerys Targaryen to <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">Khal</a></i> <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a> – succeeded<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> after years of planning.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Gift Daenerys three fossilized dragon eggs – successful,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> albeit with an unexpected outcome, she hatches them into three living <a href=\"/index.php/Dragons\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragons\">dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>To keep <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio%27s_manse\" title=\"Illyrio&#39;s manse\">his manse</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> – failed, Viserys chose to accompany Daenerys and her new husband.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>To have Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a> informing on Daenerys and Viserys. Beginning the day Dany married <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a> – successful until Dany finds this out in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Expects Daenerys to die quickly among the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> – unexpected outcome, she thrives.</li>\n<li>Plot for Prince Viserys Targaryen to join the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a> with fifty thousand Dothraki screamers at his back<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> – failed, Drogo kills Viserys<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> and then Drogo dies after suffering an infected wound.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_plans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>At some point Illyrio gets word that Daenerys has hatched three dragons, inevitably changing his plans.</li>\n<li>Send exiled Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> to join <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup> – successful.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_plans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Bring Queen Daenerys Targaryen back to <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> with her hatchling dragons<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup> – failed, she instead sails to <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a> and leaves a string of burning cities in her wake.</li>\n<li>Plans for the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a> to join Daenerys Targaryen, a pliable young child queen in <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> – failed, Daenerys ends up in Slaver's Bay and chooses to remain in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_plans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Tristan_Rivers_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ae/Tristan_Rivers_TheMico.jpg/300px-Tristan_Rivers_TheMico.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"424\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/a/ae/Tristan_Rivers_TheMico.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Tristan_Rivers_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Tristan_Rivers\" title=\"Tristan Rivers\">Tristan Rivers</a> says he has had enough of Illyrio's plans. Art by TheMico ©</div></div></div>\n<ul><li>Send <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> to meet up with Daenerys Targaryen<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup> via <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup> – partially failed, Tyrion meets up with Jon Connington, but is later kidnapped by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Deliver <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio%27s_chests\" title=\"Illyrio&#39;s chests\">six oaken chests</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Griff\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Griff\">Griff</a> – successful.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Plans to remain in Pentos to \"smooth the way\" for Daenerys Targaryen, Jon Connington, Tyrion, and the Golden Company, once they all meet in <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd5.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> – partially failed, no meeting in Volantis.</li>\n<li>Plans for the Golden Company to meet Daenerys at <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a> – failed, the Queen remains in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> while the Golden Company stop at <a href=\"/index.php/Volon_Therys\" title=\"Volon Therys\">Volon Therys</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Marry Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(Young_Griff)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (Young Griff)\">Aegon</a> to his aunt: <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> remembers secret plans with the Golden Company's previous captain-general, <a href=\"/index.php/Myles_Toyne\" title=\"Myles Toyne\">Myles Toyne</a>. They plotted with Illyrio to eventually have \"Young Griff\", whom they claim is Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Rhaegar)\">Aegon Targaryen</a>, marry Daenerys and claim the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>. Jon is unsure if Myles's successor, <a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Strickland\" title=\"Harry Strickland\">Harry Strickland</a>, is aware of the plan<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> – failed, <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tyrion\">Tyrion</a> suggests a different course of action to Aegon: head to Westeros instead of going east,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup> and Aegon decides to <a href=\"/index.php/Landing_of_the_Golden_Company\" title=\"Landing of the Golden Company\">head to Westeros</a> with the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_plans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Did he weep for <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys</a>, or for the plans he had made with him?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_17-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-17\">&#91;17&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Very little of what the <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">the fat man</a> has anticipated has come to pass. I have danced to the fat man's pipes for years, Lemore.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Lemore\" title=\"Lemore\">Lemore</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Which plan? <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">The fat man's</a> plan? The one that changes every time the <a href=\"/index.php/Moon\" title=\"Moon\">moon</a> turns?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tristan_Rivers\" title=\"Tristan Rivers\">Tristan Rivers</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I have had enough of <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio's</a> plans. <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> won the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> without the benefit of <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a>. We can do the same. And if I am wrong and <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">the realm</a> does not rise for us, we can always retreat back across the <a href=\"/index.php/Narrow_sea\" title=\"Narrow sea\">narrow sea</a>, as <a href=\"/index.php/Bittersteel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bittersteel\">Bittersteel</a> once did, and others after him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tristan_Rivers\" title=\"Tristan Rivers\">Tristan Rivers</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Illyrio%27s_plans&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_